high_descs: Look down.
Take a step forward and grab the knife in the sink.
Turn left and walk a step.  Face the left sink.
Slice the potato in the sink.
Turn right and walk to the right sink.
Put the knife down to the right of the spatula in the sink.
Turn left and walk to the left sink.
Pick up a slice of potato from the sink.
Turn around and take a step forward.  Turn left and and walk to the microwave.
Open the microwave door, put the potato slice inside on the plate, turn it on, open the door, and remove the potato slice.
Turn around and walk to the table.  Turn right at the table and walk to the refrigerator.
Open both doors and put the potato in the refrigerator on the top shelf.  Close both doors.
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato, cook it in the microwave, and put it in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Step forward to face the sink.
Pick up the knife in the sink.
Take a step to the left to face the potato in the left side of the sink.
Cut the potato in the left side of the sink into slices.
Take a step to the right to face the right side of the sink.
Place the knife in the right side of the sink.
Take a step to the left to face the potato in the left side of the sink.
Pick up a slice of potato in the sink.
Turn right and walk across the room to face the microwave.
Heat the potato slice in the microwave and remove it.
Turn around and cross the room and turn right to face the fridge.
Place the potato slice in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: To heat a potato slice and place it in the fridge.

high_descs: Go to the sink on the right
Pick up the knife in the sink
Move a bit to the left
Slice the potato in the left sink
Move a bit to the right
Put the knife in the sink
Move a bit to the left
Pick up a potato slice
Turn around, go forward a bit, turn left and go to the microwave
Put the potato slice in the microwave, start the microwave, wait, pick up the potato slice from the microwave
Turn around, go to the table, turn right, go to the fridge
Put the potato slice in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato, cook a slice of potato, put it in the fridge
